  <div class="top">Get to market a lot faster</div>
  <div class="middle">By learning to build your own apps</div>
  <div class="bottom">Knowing tech can be your secret weapon to launch great ideas quickly</div>
</h1>


<div class="holder">
  <div class="form section blue entrepreneur-section">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <h2>If you are going to make money from tech</h2>

        <p>It is important that you have at least enough development
        knowledge to be dangerous. You will have a much better idea of what
        your tech sub-contractors are up to, how long things take to build
