        <p>You will learn how to be agile and to pivot when needed and how
        to build minimum viable products. You will also get the inside scoop
        on things like SEO, data scraping and mining, and upcoming tech.</p>

        <p>All of this will become weaponry for your arsenal and will help 
        you launch products and services in less time, with far less 
        budget, and you will have a better understanding of the data.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section entrepreneur-section">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <h3>Life on the fast-track</h3>
        <p>As an Entrepreneur you can enroll as a normal student, and tell us that
        your goal is to build apps fast and to prototype your ideas and get them up
        on the web. We will give you the fast track idea genius version of the course!</p>

        <p>You want to build stuff and not try to get CS degree and we understand that.
        Devschool in fact, was founded and bootstrapped and kick-started by its founder,
        Jim - and he was only able to do it because every line of code that needed coding
        was coded by him!</p>

        <p>Your Instructor will narrow your focus to the tools you need to realize your
        dreams and give you the tools to succeed. And as someone wanting to change the 
        world, you can appreciate having the right palette and tool-set to do so!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
    <h2 class="text-center">Check out our online coding bootcamp to learn more about how to 
    <a href="/coding-bootcamp">get started today!</a></h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

